en (2014/2015\u20132015/2016)</ref>\n|align=\"center\" colspan=\"10\" style=\"color:#cccccc;\"| Tournament Not Held\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\"| Minor-Rank.\n|align=\"center\" style=\"color:#cccccc;\"|A\n|align=\"center\" style=\"color:#cccccc;\"|A\n|align=\"center\" style=\"background:#afeeee;\"|[[2018 Riga Masters|2R]]\n|align=\"center\" style=\"color:#cccccc;\"|A\n|-\n|style=\"background:#EFEFEF;\"| {{nowrap|[[International Championship]]}} \n| colspan=\"8\" style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\"|Tournament Not Held\n| align=\"center\" style=\"color:#cccccc;\"| LQ\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#ffebcd;\"|[[2013 International Championship|QF]]\n| align=\"center\" style=\"color:#cccccc;\"| LQ\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#afeeee;\"|[[2015 International Championship|2R]]\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#afeeee;\"|[[2016 International Championship|3R]]\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#afeeee;\"|[[2017 International Championship|3R]]\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#afeeee;\"|[[2018 International Championship (snooker)|1R]]\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#afeeee;\"|[[2019 International Championship (snooker)|3R]]\n|-\n|style=\"background:#EFEFEF;\"| [[China Championship (snooker)|China Championship]]\n|align=\"center\" colspan=\"12\" style=\"color:#cccccc;\"| Tournament Not Held\n|align=\"center\" style=\"color:#cccccc;\"|NR\n|align=\"center\" style=\"color:#cccccc;\"|LQ\n|align=\"center\" style=\"background:#afeeee;\"|[[2018 China Championship|3R]]\n|align=\"center\" style=\"color:#cccccc;\"|LQ\n|-\n|style=\"background:#EFEFEF;\"| [[English Open (snooker)|English Open]]\n|align=\"center\" colspan=\"12\" style=\"color:#cccccc;\"| Tournament Not Held\n|align=\"center\" style=\"background:#00ff00;\"|[[2016 English Open (snooker)|'''W''']]\n|align=\"center\" style=\"background:#afeeee;\"|[[2017 English Open (snooker)|3R]]\n|align=\"center\" style=\"background:#afeeee;\"|[[2018 English Open (snooker)|2R]]\n|align=\"center\" style=\"background:#afeeee;\"|[[2019 English Open (snooker)|1R]]\n|-\n|style=\"background:#EFEFEF;\" | [[World Open (snooker)|World Open]]<ref group=\"nb\">The event was called the Grand Prix (1998/1999\u20132000/2001 and 2004/2005\u20132009/2010), the LG Cup (2001/2002\u20132003/2004) and the Haikou World Open (2011/2012\u20132013/2014)</ref>\n| align=\"center\" style=\"color:#cccccc;\"| A\n| align=\"center\" style=\"color:#cccccc;\"| LQ\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#afeeee;\"|[[2006 Grand Prix (snooker)|RR]]\n| align=\"center\" style=\"color:#cccccc;\"| LQ\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#afeeee;\"|[[2008 Grand Prix (snooker)|1R]]\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#afeeee;\"|[[2009 Grand Prix (snooker)|1R]]\n| align=\"center\" style=\"color:#cccccc;\"| LQ\n| align=\"center\" style=\"color:#cccccc;\"| LQ\n| align=\"center\" style=\"color:#cccccc;\"| LQ\n| align=\"center\" style=\"background:#afeeee;\"|[[2014 World Open (snooker)|3R]]\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\"|Not Held\n| align=\"center\" style=\"background:#afeeee;\"|[[2016 World Open (snooker)|2R]]\n| align=\"center\" style=\"background:#afeeee;\"|[[2017 World Open (snooker)|1R]]\n| align=\"center\" style=\"color:#cccccc;\"| LQ\n| align=\"center\" style=\"background:#afeeee;\"|[[2019 World Open (snooker)|2R]]\n|-\n|style=\"background:#EFEFEF;\"| [[Northern Ireland Open (snooker)|Northern Ireland Open]]\n| align=\"center\" colspan=\"12\" style=\"color:#cccccc;\"| Tournament Not Held\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#afeeee;\"|[[2016 Northern Ireland Open|2R]]\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#afeeee;\"|[[2017 Northern Ireland Open|2R]]\n| align=\"center\" style=\"color:#cccccc;\"|WD\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#afeeee;\"|[[2019 Northern Ireland Open|2R]]\n|-\n|style=\"background:#EFEFEF;\"| [[UK Championship (snooker)|UK Championship]]\n| align=\"center\" style=\"color:#cccccc;\"| A\n